## Phase 1 — Embedding Pipeline Hardening & Smart Chunking

**Goal**: Make the vector store actually useful with real embeddings and metadata-rich chunks.

### [MODIFY] [embedding_tool.py](file:///c:/Users/Relanto/OneDrive%20-%20Relanto/Desktop/hack/backend/tools/embedding_tool.py)
- Remove `USE_MOCK_EMBEDDINGS` default override
- Add a `USE_REAL_EMBEDDINGS` mode that lazy-loads `BAAI/bge-large-en-v1.5` on first call
- Add embedding cache (LRU) to avoid re-encoding identical chunks
- Add batch encoding method `get_embeddings(texts: list)` for bulk indexing performance
- Keep mock fallback but make it opt-in, not opt-out

### [MODIFY] [chunking.py](file:///c:/Users/Relanto/OneDrive%20-%20Relanto/Desktop/hack/backend/rag/chunking.py)
- Add **section-aware chunking**: respect section boundaries so chunks don't span Risk Factors into MD&A
- Add **metadata-enriched chunking**: each chunk returns `{text, metadata}` where metadata includes `section_name`, `chunk_index`, `char_start`, `char_end`, `filing_company`, `filing_type`
- Add **overlap sentence deduplication**: when chunks overlap, detect and tag duplicate sentences
- Add **parent-child chunking**: store both a larger "parent" chunk (1400 chars) and smaller "child" chunks (700 chars) — retrieve child, expand to parent for context

### [MODIFY] [chroma_tool.py](file:///c:/Users/Relanto/OneDrive%20-%20Relanto/Desktop/hack/backend/tools/chroma_tool.py)
- Support **collection-per-report** via `get_or_create_collection(report_id)` — isolates document namespaces
- Add `add_chunks_batch()` that accepts pre-computed embeddings for bulk performance
- Add richer metadata schema: `company`, `section`, `chunk_index`, `parent_chunk_id`, `filing_date`, `filing_type`
- Add `delete_collection(report_id)` for cleanup
- Keep the global "filings" collection as a cross-report search index

### [MODIFY] [langgraph_flow.py](file:///c:/Users/Relanto/OneDrive%20-%20Relanto/Desktop/hack/backend/graph/langgraph_flow.py) (node_ingest_and_chunk)
- Pass enriched metadata from section extractor through to ChromaDB
- Store chunks in both report-scoped collection and global collection
- Track `report_id` in AgentState

### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///c:/Users/Relanto/OneDrive%20-%20Relanto/Desktop/hack/backend/main.py)
- Remove `os.environ.setdefault("USE_MOCK_EMBEDDINGS", "true")` — let config determine embedding mode
- Add environment variable `EMBEDDING_MODE=real|mock` with `mock` as default for fast dev, `real` for production

